ons with Robert ll d'Estouteville. She died in Cottingham, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"about 1045–":"umbes 1045–Surnud","1040–1107":"1040–1107","1075–1140":"1075–1140","1088–Male":"1088–Surnud","1091–Male":"1091–Surnud","1045–Female":"1045–Surnud","1091":"1091","1107":"1107","1100":"1100","1045":"1045","1088":"1088","1385":"1385","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","1040":"1040","about 1075":"umbes 1075","about 1045":"umbes 1045","Cottingham, Yorkshire, England":"Cottingham, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Newbold on Avon, Warwickshire, England":"Newbold on Avon, Warwickshire, England","Valmont, Le Havre, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, France":"Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Estouteville, Normandy, France":"Estouteville, Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1045–":"noin 1045–Kuollut","1040–1107":"1040–1107","1075–1140":"1075–1140","1088–Male":"1088–Kuollut","1091–Male":"1091–Kuollut","1045–Female":"1045–Kuollut","1091":"1091","1107":"1107","1100":"1100","1045":"1045","1088":"1088","1385":"1385","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","1040":"1040","about 1075":"noin 1075","about 1045":"noin 1045","Cottingham, Yorkshire, England":"Cottingham, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Newbold on Avon, Warwickshire, England":"Newbold on Avon, Warwickshire, England","Valmont, Le Havre, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, France":"Valmont, Seine-Maritime, Haute-Normandie, Ranska","Estouteville, Normandy, France":"Estouteville, Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1045–":"environ 1045–Décédée","1040–1107":"1040–1107","1075–1140":"1075–1140","1088–Male":"1088–Décédé","1091–Male":"1091–Décédé","1045–Female":"1045–Décédée","1091":"1091","1107":"1107","1100":"1100","1045":"1045","1088":"1088","1385":"1385","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","1040":"1040","about 1075":"environ 1075","about 1045":"environ 1045","Cottingham, Yorkshire, England":"Cottingham, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Newbold on Avon, Warwickshire, England":"Newbold on Avon, Warwi